m)","250 g cherry tomatoes (1 punnet), cut into halves","2 pinches sea salt","2 pinches ground black pepper","1 brown onion, cut into halves","1 leek (approx. 110 g), trimmed and cut into pieces","120 g bacon, cut into pieces"]},{"title":"Velouté sauce","content":["3 - 5 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only","30 g unsalted butter","30 g plain flour","130 g water","1 tsp Vegetable stock paste (see Tips)","70 g sour cream or pouring (whipping) cream"]},{"title":"Mashed potato","content":["50 g Parmesan cheese, crust removed and cut into pieces (3 cm)","1000 g floury potatoes (e.g. Red Pontiac, Royal Blue), peeled and cut into pieces (2-3 cm)","½ - 1 tsp salt, to taste","250 g full cream milk","30 g butter, plus extra for shaving","1 - 2 pinches ground nutmeg (optional)"]}],"id":"r79003","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-ok6ivInbs78\/XZVQ8rT2PYI\/AAAAAAAAdHw\/mTqD1Jj50fALQaIs5iGGL8oy4hNSf1HygCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_aQyocGldEicfcD7Q.png","title":"Fish pie with mashed potato topping","publishedAt":"2015-08-07T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"34 g","fat":"26 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"30 g","calories":"2097 kJ \/ 499 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking dish (22 x 30 cm), bowl, oven, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","2h","6 portions"]}